Function 00h	Reset - reset the disk controller chip
entry	AH	00h
	DL	drive (if bit 7 is set both hard disks and floppy disks reset)
		00h-7Fh  floppy disk
		80h-0FFh hard disk
return	AH	status (see 01h below)
